<item>
            <title>[LU-5829] too many EXPORT_SYMBOL in code</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5829</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Lustre currently exports 1809 symbols, compared to 25395 symbols for the whole linux kernel.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A lot of these symbols don&apos;t need to be exported at all because they are only used in the module they belong to.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="27387">LU-5829</key>
            <summary>too many EXPORT_SYMBOL in code</summary>
