                            <comment id="160502" author="panda" created="Tue, 2 Aug 2016 07:42:07 +0000"  >&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;frank zago (fzago@cray.com) uploaded a new patch: &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/13323&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/13323&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This patch is not correct. It removes e.g. lu_ref_add() export, but it is used from other modules (you can check with grep).&lt;br/&gt;
Builds with --enable-lu_ref are broken because of this change.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
